===Etymology 1===
{{ja-kanjitab|がい|yomi=kanon|alt=崕}}

From {{der|ja|ltc|sort=かい'|-}} {{ltc-l|崖|[[cliff]], [[precipice]]}}. Not attested in isolation. First attested in compound {{m|ja|崖岸|tr=gaigan||cliff shore, cliff bank}} in 900.<ref name="KDJ2-gaigan">{{R:Nihon Kokugo Daijiten 2|崖岸}}</ref>

====Pronunciation====
